entry.title: 2835 White LED Strip Light High-CRI - 12V - IP20 - 278 Lumens/ft with Driver and Controller (KIT)
entry.summary:
Vendor: LEDMyplace Canada
Type: Single Color LED Strip Lights
Price: 130.81

Here’s a 5-meter LED strip lights that await to adorn the indoor spaces of your home and office. This 57.75 watts stip light is available in three color temperature options: 3000K, 4000K and 6500K. The strip light comes with an IP20 rating which makes it suitable for indoor conditions. Having a 10mm PCB, this strip light, and a 3M adhesive tape backing, it will offer an easy installation. It comes with 60 LEDs per meter and will operate on a 12-volt power supply. Along with the strip light, you will get a 72W desktop type driver having an input range of 100-240 Volts AC current. In this kit, you also get a Single Color Wireless Controller which works on 12-24 Volts DC current and receives RF signals from compatible wireless LED dimmer wall switch.
